These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, juice
House: colonial, tower, palace, victorian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, dannemann, bolivar, aristoff
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, dancing, singing, board-games
 1. the colonial house is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the aristoff-smoker is the tower house##1
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 6. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the palace house##3
10. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person drinking almond-milk##7
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
12. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | juice    | coffee | fanta    | almond-milk   |
| House   | colonial | palace | tower | victorian |
| Cigar           | dannemann       | bolivar   | aristoff  | pall-mall     |
| Hobby     | gardening      | singing   | board-games    | dancing    |

