 1. the person playing whist is the fan country##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan country##1
 3. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the fan folk##1
 5. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 7. the fan country is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person playing snooker##7
 8. the fan trance is not the person playing bridge##6
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
10. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
12. the fan country is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Music-Genre         | metal      | country   | trance   | folk       |
| Transport   | subway | train    | roller | trike       |
| Birthday   | february  | december | january   | october     |
| Game         | bridge   | whist    | snooker   | backgammon |

