.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, motorbike, trike
House: palace, colonial, townhouse, farmhouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, family, scientific, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, american, brazilian, british
 1. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the british is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
 3. the person watching animation movies is between the british and the brazilian##2
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the palace house##1
 5. the colonial house is not the american##6
 6. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the farmhouse house##7
 8. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
 9. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
10. the colonial house is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person driving the tram is the townhouse house##1
12. the townhouse house is not the brazilian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Transport   | skateboard   | trike     | motorbike   | tram |
| House       | farmhouse   | palace | colonial | townhouse    |
| Movie-Genre      | scientific | animation | disaster   | family  |
| Nationality        | british | mexican     | brazilian   | american |

