.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, azure, apricot, blue
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, russian, italian, polish
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, dog, frog
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia, aconite, lily
 1. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
 2. the person who growsazalea is between the italian and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
 5. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who growsbegonia is not the owner of the dog##6
 7. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the polish and the malaysian##7
 8. the person who growsazalea is not the malaysian##6
 9. the owner of the frog is not the polish##6
10. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
11. the russian is on the right of the person who growslily##1
12. the italian is not the person who likes azure##6
13. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
14. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
15. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Color      | azure      | ivory        | blue          | apricot    |
| Nationality         | polish | russian    | italian          | malaysian |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | bird   | dog | frog      |
| Flower   | lily       | azalea | aconite          | begonia        |

