.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, dahlia, balloon-flower, azalea
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, ship, skateboard, train
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, may, february
City: marseilles, new-york, london, rome
 1. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
 2. the person driving the skateboard is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growsdahlia##2
 5. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person who growsdaffodil##7
 7. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Flower   | azalea      | balloon-flower     | dahlia   | daffodil    |
| Transport     | train | skateboard   | ship | airplane |
| Birthday     | february        | may     | september  | april      |
| City   | new-york       | rome | marseilles   | london    |

 